node.text: Since the comedy of my last post went over a few heads, here's some teasers for my novel. You've trusted me as your source for cathartic laughter, do you trust me to take you on a wild, addicting, sexy fictional adventure? Come see more @mementomoribook (link for book in bio) #bookstagram #dantegabrielrossetti #rossetti #williammorris #mementomori #mementomoribook #preraphaelites #preraphaelitebrotherhood #romancebooks #romancelandia #historicalromance #romancebooksofinstagram

Photo by Teacher Misery on July 18, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'was asked to help monitor a small group of students with accommodations during state testing, by admin. I was called in a week later and written up for dereliction of duties because I wasn't with my own students during testing.... but was with the group admin had assigned to me.'.

Photo by Teacher Misery on July 18, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Notes Done filed a complaint about my grades being changed with screen shots of my grades that put in the system along with the fear of being retaliated against. was told that it was illegal ....... bla bla ....... not even two days later. My principal observed me in class has yet to provide me with feedback but at 345 that same day gave me a 48hour notice of a meeting with him that I was being accused of corporal punishment. Talk about retaliation alright and now have to wait till Tuesday to find out what this "accusation" is'.

Photo by Teacher Misery on July 18, 2021. May be an image of flower and text that says 'was just diagnosed with Type 1 Diabetes in April. My blood sugar was consistently in the red due to all the added stress put on teaching in person during pandemic, including being asked to be mentor teacher and coach a sport last minute. Even though shared with admin.i was going through a rough time. I've had consistently great glucose numbers during break. I'm literally afraid to go back for my health.'.

Photo by Teacher Misery on July 18, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'My father died in the fall & my admin told my parents I wasn't on my "A" game. She even wrote in my eval that I struggled bouncing back after the death of my father. left teaching after that, and haven't been stressed out since.'.

Photo by Teacher Misery on July 18, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'to a a Tomorrow I am going fertility doctor for second opinion. The office is an hour away so I will be taking the entire day off of work. I am 43 and it's not looking good for me. I will probably be given devastating news, but it's still better than going to my job at a completely dysfunctional private school.'.
